symf.name: KEY_CREATE_SUB_KEY
symf.desc: Required to create a subkey of a registry key

symf.name: KEY_ENUMERATE_SUB_KEYS
symf.desc: Required to enumerate the subkeys of a registry key

symf.name: KEY_NOTIFY
symf.desc: Required to request change notifications for a registry key or for subkeys of a registry key

symf.name: KEY_QUERY_VALUE
symf.desc: Required to query the values of a registry key

symf.name: KEY_SET_VALUE
symf.desc: Required to create, delete, or set a registry value

symf.name: KEY_WOW64_32KEY
symf.desc: Indicates that an application on 64-bit Windows should operate on the 32-bit registry view. This flag is ignored by 32-bit Windows

symf.name: KEY_WOW64_64KEY
symf.desc: Indicates that an application on 64-bit Windows should operate on the 64-bit registry view. This flag is ignored by 32-bit Windows
